rs</h2><div class="variablelist"><dl><dt><span class="term"><i><tt>name</tt></i></span></dt><dd>
						ASCII character string to display in the menu entry.
					</dd><dt><span class="term"><i><tt>value</tt></i></span></dt><dd>
						Value to return to the menu's callback function if the menu entry is selected.
					</dd></dl></div></div><div class="refsect1" lang="en"><a name="glutAddMenuEntry.3GLUT-description"/><h2>Description</h2><p>
			<tt>glutAddMenuEntry</tt> adds a menu entry to the bottom of the current menu. The string name will be
			displayed for the newly added menu entry. If the menu entry is selected by the user, the menu's callback will be called
			passing value as the callback's parameter.
